project.name: Spine_Case_Study_A4
project.description: Spine Toolbox project for the workflow of case study A4, aiming to demonstrate some key functionality required for replicating RealValue project results.

Building_Data_Store.description: Contains Spine Model compatible building model input, as well as the output from the building model.

Power_Data_Store.description: Database for power system Spine Model input data.

Combined_Data_Store.description: Data store for the combined input data from the building and power system models.

Power_Data_Connection.description: Raw data for the power system model.

Power_Model.description: Runs Spine Model with the power system database

BM2UC.description: Modifies power system input using building model results

Combined_Model.description: Runs Spine Model with the combined building and power system database.

Building_Data_Importer.description: Imports raw building data into the database.

Power_Data_Importer.description: Imports raw power system data into a Spine Model compatible database.
